{"tid":2272232,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：期待不反共的美國政府 美中合作發大財","createTime":"2020-11-05T03:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T03:19:01.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a291a8c97e04f0a0b3d288227c0a08230e1aa46b","tid":2272232,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T03:04:44.000Z","msg":"中國外交部期望美方新一屆政府能夠與中方相向而行<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部副部長樂玉成表示，很關注美國大選，選票仍在統計，結果尚未確定，但希望大選能夠平穩、順利舉行。<br />\n<br />\n樂玉成出席一個吹風會時說，中方一貫明確認為，雖然中美存在一些分歧，但擁有廣泛的共同利益和合作空間，保持和推動中美關係健康穩定發展，不僅符合兩國人民根本利益，也是國際社會的共同期待。<br />\n<br />\n樂玉成期望，美方新一屆政府能夠與中方相向而行，秉持不衝突、不對抗、相互尊重、合作共贏的精神，兩國有很多合作的地方，應該聚焦合作、管控分歧，推動兩國關係沿正確軌道向前發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558483-20201105.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558483-20201105.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4IuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=5336d331\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558483-20201105.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1bc91690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558483-20201105.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f10492fa2978842713811baa203f1df87f00e50a","tid":2272232,"uid":229019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"一齊玩幻奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434f7ac36468491030086f2399fc8102408682ea","tid":2272232,"uid":229019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f10492fa2978842713811baa203f1df87f00e50a","tid":2272232,"uid":229019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"一齊玩幻奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T03:18:38.000Z","msg":"幻幼"},{"pid":"3cbcdfd7567ca4c2c1442f1a5d35c3de8ad6e111","tid":2272232,"uid":229019,"like":0,"dis